  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to tap to disable a network **so that** I can prevent asset transfers through that specific network, ensuring security and avoiding accidental or unwanted transactions.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nFigma Design 1: https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2388-503644&mode=design&t=V0dXiJUCqM0Jo7Od-4\r\nFigma Design 2: https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2396-514803&mode=design&t=V0dXiJUCqM0Jo7Od-4\r\nFigma Design 3: https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2436-520431&mode=design&t=V0dXiJUCqM0Jo7Od-4\r\n\r\nVisual reference:\r\n<img width=\"185\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/18485527/2379c831-f5da-40dd-be2e-bbf824c541b2\"> <img width=\"185\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/18485527/f908f21b-bd1b-4cb9-b9be-f8006553616b\"> <img width=\"185\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/18485527/bdf31279-22f8-4275-a3e9-ce71342c2444\">\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- [ ] When user taps on a network card, it should be toggle its enabled / disabled state\r\n- [ ] Network breakdown and fees should be re-calculated every time a network is disabled on enabled",
